INSERT INTO webauthn_credentials 
        (platform_id, credential_id, public_key_cose, counter, user_handle, is_active, created_at)
        VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, TRUE, NOW())
        ON CONFLICT (credential_id) 
        DO UPDATE SET 
            counter = EXCLUDED.counter,
            last_used_at = NOW()
